      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=p9f77egj0r]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=p9f77egj0r]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=uetgkxvm8h]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=uetgkxvm8h]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"p9f77egj0r\">Project</span></strong>: Taraji</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"uetgkxvm8h\">Scene by</span></strong>: <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://alejandroalvarez.artstation.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Alejandro Alvarez</a></p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://downloads.renderman.pixar.com/resources/Tajari/Tajari_RfM.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"DownloadButton2.png\" width=\"158\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611680348/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627700666&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/611680348/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627700666&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"611680402\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"DownloadButton2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"611680348\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"3158cdb4-f74f-4630-9d26-279a79a442f2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611680348/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627700666&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611680348/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627700666&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37 1x\" /></span></a><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://downloads.renderman.pixar.com/resources/Tajari/Taraji_RfH.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"DownloadButton2.png\" width=\"158\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611680348/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627700666&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/611680348/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627700666&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"611680402\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"DownloadButton2.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"611680348\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"3158cdb4-f74f-4630-9d26-279a79a442f2\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611680348/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627700666&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611680348/DownloadButton2.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627700666&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=158&amp;height=37 1x\" /></span></a></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<h2 id=\"Taraji-Overview\">Overview</h2><p>Taraji is the creation of artist Alejandro Alvarez and was achieved using Zbrush, Maya, Substance 3D Painter, and RenderMan.</p><p>Taraji means Hope in Swahili. Her jewels, makeup, and clothes are a great way to explore different materials in RenderMan. The skin material was developed using the best practices at Pixar for skin rendering, so download the asset and have fun learning!<br />.</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"Taraji.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611680348/Taraji.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627769619&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=950\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/611680348/Taraji.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627769619&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"3000\" data-width=\"2400\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"611319930\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"Taraji.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"611680348\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"6e269980-6f62-431e-9b5c-3efbf5ff20e4\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611680348/Taraji.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627769619&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=1520&amp;height=1900 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611680348/Taraji.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627769619&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=950 1x\" /></span><hr /><h3 style=\"text-align: center;\" id=\"Taraji-AbouttheArtist\">About the Artist</h3><a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://alejandroalvarez.artstation.com/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"alejandro-alvarez-headshot.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611680348/alejandro-alvarez-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627790497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/611680348/alejandro-alvarez-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627790497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"512\" data-width=\"512\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"611352769\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"alejandro-alvarez-headshot.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"611680348\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"2\" data-media-id=\"9349ae9a-63e4-484d-9f35-385519893ce6\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611680348/alejandro-alvarez-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627790497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=400&amp;height=400 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/611680348/alejandro-alvarez-headshot.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758627790497&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=200 1x\" /></span></a><p>Alejandro Alvarez is a 3D artist with a background in industrial design. During the last 13 years he&rsquo;s collaborated in many projects, while working in different production roles. He&rsquo;s currently a Senior 3D Character Artist.</p><hr /><p>This project is available with an Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International License. This allows you to share and redistribute for non-commercial purposes, provided that you credit the original author.</p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"73f2ea8e-82d8-4ec9-81c8-d867b8d28648\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\"><h3 id=\"Taraji-Attribution-NonCommercial4.0International(CCBY-NC4.0)\">Attribution-NonCommercial 4.0 International (CC BY-NC 4.0)</h3></div></div><p /><p /><p /><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>"
